title: Gorilla Position: AJ Styles
text:
WWE Gorilla Position: Listen as AJ Styles joins James Delow Last Updated: 23/03/17 5:32pm Gorilla Position AJ Styles is GP's special guest as he reveals his dream opponent, while the gang discuss the build-up to Wrestlemania. 
Hot on the heels of an exclusive chat with Luke Harper last week, it's the turn of 'The Phenomenal One' to talk to our esteemed host and he has plenty to say on his upcoming Mania showdown with Shane McMahon as well as the fan's reaction to the match. 
Listen to the show and flick back through the Gorilla Position archives right here: http://www.skysports.com/podcasts/gorilla-position Dates for WWE's upcoming pay-per-views 
Matt Davies, Skillit and Ash Rose are on hand to wade through all the WWE week and the Wrestlemania sub-plots that continue to bubble ahead of the main event which is less than two weeks away. 
The boys offer their in-depth thoughts on Roman's programme with the Undertaker, the friendship fall-out between Chris Jericho and Kevin Owens, the Raw opening segment fireworks between Stephanie McMahon and Mick Foley and the spectacular head-to-head between Shane and Styles. 
All this plus lots of major news stories hitting the headlines, so sit back, relax, crack open a cold one and get into the Gorilla Position! 
Don't miss it! http://www.skysports.com/podcasts/gorilla-position
